No. 10-6920. Phillip L. Harmon, Petitioner v. Tim Anderson, Sheriff, Santa Barbara County, California, et al. 562 U.S. 1124,131 S. Ct. 828,

178 L. Ed. 2d 579,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 9752. December 13, 2010.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.

Justice Breyer took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 384 Fed. Appx. 673.
